# Local development secrets — loaded automatically by `aai dev`.
# Copy this to .env and fill in your values. The .env file is gitignored.
#
# For production, use `aai secret put <NAME>` to set secrets on the server.
# In both cases, access secrets in agent code via ctx.env.MY_KEY.
#
# ASSEMBLYAI_API_KEY is managed globally by the CLI (~/.config/aai/).
# Run `aai init` to set up your API key, or set it manually in ~/.config/aai/config.json.
#
# Add any additional secrets your agent needs below:
